#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.store"
msgstr "# triton.language.store"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:4
msgid "原型："
msgstr "Prototype:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.store(\n"
" pointer,\n"
" value,\n"
" mask=None,\n"
" boundary_check=(),\n"
" cache_modifier='',\n"
" eviction_policy='',\n"
" _semantic=None\n"
")\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:8
msgid "简介：将一个Tensor/Scalar从UnifiedBuffer按照`pointer`所指的地址存回GlobalMemory"
msgstr "Introduction: Store a Tensor/Scalar from UnifiedBuffer back to GlobalMemory according to the address pointed to by `pointer`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:10
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:12
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:14
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `pointer`        | `triton.PointerType` <br> 或 `tensor<triton.PointerType>` <br> 或`triton.PointerType<tensor>`（来源于`tl.make_block_ptr`）         | 指向GM上待存储地址的指针                                                    |\n"
"| `value`       | `tensor` 或 `scalar`  | 要存储的值，支持隐式广播和隐式类型转换  |\n"
"| `mask`       | `int1`或`tensor<int1>`    | 可选参数，当且仅当`pointer` 不来源于`tl.make_block_ptr`时可传入<br>若`mask[i]==False` ，则不会将`value[i]`存储到`pointer[i]`指向的地址,是`True`则正常存储 <br>若`pointer`来源于`tl.make_block_ptr`，则`mask`必须是`None`                                        |\n"
"| `boundary_check` | `tuple(int)` | 可选参数，当且仅当`pointer`来源于`tl.make_block_ptr`时可传入<br>整数元组，指示需要做边界检查的维度                                         |\n"
"| `cache_modifier`   | `\"\"` 或 `\"ca\"`或`\"cg\"`                | 可选参数，控制NVIDIA PTX上的cache选项，对Ascend硬件无效                                                |\n"
"| `eviction_policy`   | `str`                | 控制NVIDIA PTX的eviction策略， 对Ascend硬件无效                                                |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                                |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ---- | ----------- |\n"
"| `pointer` | `triton.PointerType` <br> or `tensor<triton.PointerType>` <br> or `triton.PointerType<tensor>` (from `tl.make_block_ptr`) | Pointer to the address on GM where data is to be stored |\n"
"| `value` | `tensor` or `scalar` | The value to be stored, supports implicit broadcasting and implicit type conversion |\n"
"| `mask` | `int1` or `tensor<int1>` | Optional parameter, can only be passed when `pointer` is not from `tl.make_block_ptr`<br>If `mask[i]==False`, `value[i]` will not be stored to the address pointed by `pointer[i]`; if `True`, normal storage occurs<br>If `pointer` is from `tl.make_block_ptr`, `mask` must be `None` |\n"
"| `boundary_check` | `tuple(int)` | Optional parameter, can only be passed when `pointer` is from `tl.make_block_ptr`<br>Integer tuple indicating which dimensions require boundary checking |\n"
"| `cache_modifier` | `\"\"` or `\"ca\"` or `\"cg\"` | Optional parameter, controls cache options on NVIDIA PTX, ineffective on Ascend hardware |\n"
"| `eviction_policy` | `str` | Controls the eviction policy on NVIDIA PTX, ineffective on Ascend hardware |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:16
msgid "返回值：无返回值"
msgstr "Return value: none"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:18
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:20
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:22
msgid ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √    | √     | √     | √     | √      | √      | √      | √     | √    | √    | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | ×    | √    |  √    |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √    | √     | √     | √     | √      | √      | √      | √     | √    | √    | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | ×    | √    | √    |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:24
msgid ""
"结论：Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持能力（硬件限制）。\n"
"专家意见：eviction_policy和cache_modifier参见load\n"
msgstr ""
"Conclusion: Ascend lacks support for uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation).  \n"
"Expert opinion: For eviction_policy and cache_modifier, refer to load.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:26
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:28
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围          |\n"
"| ------ | --------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 支持scalar和1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend | 支持scalar和1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Supports scalar and 1~5D tensors |\n"
"| Ascend | Supports scalar and 1~5D tensors |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:30
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms, both support 1 to 5-dimensional tensors."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:32
msgid "#### 2.2.3 社区约束"
msgstr "#### 2.2.3 Community Constraints"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:34
msgid ""
"1. 若`pointer`是一个单指针：\n"
"   - 此时`value`和`mask`必须是一个标量\n"
"   - `other`会隐式类型转换成`pointer.dtype.element_ty`的数据类型\n"
"   - 此时不允许传入`boundary_check`\n"
"2. 若`pointer`是一个N-Dimensional tensor：\n"
"   - `mask`和`value`会隐式广播到和`pointer`相同的shape\n"
"   - 此时不允许传入`boundary_check`\n"
"3. 若`pointer`来自于`tl.make_block_ptr`:\n"
"   - 此时`mask` 必须是None\n"
"   - 此时可以通过`boundary_check`设置边界检查\n"
msgstr ""
"1. If `pointer` is a single pointer:  \n"
"   - In this case, `value` and `mask` must be scalars.  \n"
"   - `other` is implicitly type-cast to the data type of `pointer.dtype.element_ty`.  \n"
"   - `boundary_check` is not allowed in this case.  \n"
"2. If `pointer` is an N-dimensional tensor:  \n"
"   - `mask` and `value` are implicitly broadcast to the same shape as `pointer`.  \n"
"   - `boundary_check` is not allowed in this case.  \n"
"3. If `pointer` comes from `tl.make_block_ptr`:  \n"
"   - In this case, `mask` must be `None`.  \n"
"   - Boundary checking can be set via `boundary_check`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:36
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:38
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability deficiency and inability to achieve"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:40
msgid "Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持能力（硬件限制）, eviction_policy和cache_modifier在NPU上功能还不完善。"
msgstr "Ascend lacks support for uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation), and the functionality of eviction_policy and cache_modifier on NPU is not yet complete."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:42
msgid ""
"| 差异点                                 | 描述                                                         | 解决途径                       |\n"
"| -------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------ |\n"
"| 离散mask的泛化性问题                   | 当前对于store中离散mask的处理，是将store拆解为atomic {load,select,store}，在corner case中存在一定泛化性问题 | 大量泛化测试暴露问题，迭代解决 |\n"
"| 与分支、循环语句搭配使用时的泛化性问题 | 当前tl.load的`pointer`和`mask`的计算过程，如果涉及较复杂的循环和分支语句，可能会出现编译问题 | 大量泛化测试暴露问题，迭代解决 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Difference | Description | Solution |\n"
"| --- | --- | --- |\n"
"| Generalization issue with discrete masks | The current handling of discrete masks in `store` decomposes the store into atomic {load, select, store} operations, which has certain generalization issues in corner cases | Expose issues through extensive generalization testing, resolve iteratively |\n"
"| Generalization issue when used with branch and loop statements | If the computation of `pointer` and `mask` in `tl.load` involves complex loops and branch statements, compilation issues may arise | Expose issues through extensive generalization testing, resolve iteratively |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:44
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:46
msgid "以下示例中通过`triton_ldst_indirect_08_kernel`和`triton_ldst_indirect_08_func`的配合调用，实现了`torch_ldst_indirect_08_func`的功能："
msgstr "In the following example, the functionality of `torch_ldst_indirect_08_func` is achieved through the coordinated invocation of `triton_ldst_indirect_08_kernel` and `triton_ldst_indirect_08_func`."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.store.md:48
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_ldst_indirect_08_kernel(\n"
"    out_ptr0, in_ptr1, in_ptr2, in_ptr3, stride_in_r,\n"
"    XS: tl.constexpr, RS: tl.constexpr\n"
"):\n"
"    pid = tl.program_id(0)\n"
"    in_idx0 = pid * XS + tl.arange(0, XS)\n"
"    in_idx1 = tl.arange(0, RS)\n"
"    tmp0 = tl.arange(0, XS)\n"
"    tmp1 = tl.load(in_ptr1 + in_idx1)\n"
"    in_idx2 = tmp0[:, None] * stride_in_r + tmp1[None, :]\n"
"    tmp2 = tl.load(in_ptr2 + in_idx2)\n"
"    tmp2 = tl_math.exp(tmp2)\n"
"    tmp3 = tl.load(in_ptr3 + in_idx1)\n"
"    tmp3 = tmp3 + 1 - 8\n"
"    out0_idx = in_idx0[:, None] * RS + tmp3[None, :]\n"
"    tl.store(out_ptr0 + out0_idx, tmp2)\n"
"\n"
"def triton_ldst_indirect_08_func(xc, x2, xs, rs): # [8-24] ori 8 16\n"
"    nr = x2.size()[0]\n"
"    nc = xc.numel()\n"
"    stride_in_r = x2.stride()[0]\n"
"    assert nr == xs, \"test only single core\"\n"
"    y0 = torch.empty((nr, nc), dtype=x2.dtype, device=x2.device)\n"
"    xc1 = xc - 1\n"
"    triton_ldst_indirect_08_kernel[nr // xs, 1, 1](\n"
"        y0, xc, x2, xc1, stride_in_r, XS = xs, RS = rs)\n"
"    return y0\n"
"\n"
"def torch_ldst_indirect_08_func(xr, xc, x2):\n"
"    flatten_idx = (xr[:, None] * x2.stride()[0] + xc[None, :]).flatten()\n"
"    extracted = x2.flatten()[flatten_idx].reshape([xr.numel(), xc.numel()])\n"
"    print(extracted)\n"
"    return torch.exp(extracted)\n"
"\n"
"DEV = \"npu\"\n"
"DTYPE = torch.float32\n"
"offset = 8\n"
"N0, N1 = 16, 32\n"
"blocksize = 8\n"
"lowdimsize = N0\n"
"assert N1 >= N0+offset, \"N1 must be >= N0+offset\"\n"
"assert N0 == lowdimsize, \"N0 must be == lowdimsize\"\n"
"xc = offset + torch.arange(0, N0, device=DEV)\n"
"xr = torch.arange(0, blocksize, device=DEV)\n"
"x2 = torch.randn((blocksize, N1), dtype=DTYPE, device=DEV)\n"
"torch_ref = torch_ldst_indirect_08_func(xr, xc, x2)\n"
"triton_cal = triton_ldst_indirect_08_func(xc, x2, blocksize, lowdimsize)\n"
"torch.testing.assert_close(triton_cal, torch_ref)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

